    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks that's helpful. i actually already have a bottle of some high strength stuff i ordered. it's 50,000 IU per pill. to make sure i'm getting the most out of it, should i take it with a meal or on an empty stomach? also, is it better to take it all at once in the morning or split it up into two doses during the day?",
